    "Overall, DeepCoro's performance was closer to two experts annotating the CAG videos, rather than the clinical report, demonstrating DeepCoro's potential as a standardized approach to assess CAG videos.",
    "Ultimately, DeepCoro's Algorithm 6 accuracy more closely mirrored the assessments of two expert cardiologists in annotating CAG videos and was superior to the conventional clinical report.",
    "To verify if the performance of our model mirrors the lower variability of QCA, we fine-tuned and tested the regression performance of our pipeline on Dataset D, a dataset of CAG videos which uses QCA assessment as ground truth.",
    "The average percentage annotated in this dataset is 33.7 ± 11.7%.",
    "Overall, the fine-tuned model had a MAE against QCA of 7.75% (95% CI: 7.37-8.07; Supplementary Table 9; Supplementary Figs. 3c and 4c)."
